                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Exit                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     move  "E"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-key
                     go to acc-cat-scr-999.
